Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rustc-@MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@ | rustc, binutils, gcc
Provides: cargo (= ${binary:Version})
Replaces: cargo
Conflicts: rustup
Description: Rust package manager @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@
 Cargo is a tool that allows Rust projects to declare their various
 dependencies and ensure repeatable builds. This package provides Cargo
 for the Rust @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@.x toolchain.
